# Rust
/target
**/*.rs.bk
**/*.bak
Cargo.lock.bak

# napi-rs build artifacts
# Generated native binaries stay out of git. This *.node rule also
# covers the binaries that land inside crates/polyops-napi/npm/<platform>/
# during a release build — only the metadata in those dirs is tracked.
*.node
*.wasm
crates/polyops-napi/index.js
crates/polyops-napi/index.d.ts
# crates/polyops-napi/npm/ is intentionally tracked (per-platform
# package.json metadata is committed; *.node inside it stays ignored).

# Node
node_modules
.npm
.pnpm-store
parity/dist
parity/goldens-tmp

# Editor / OS
.idea
.vscode
*.swp
.DS_Store

# Coverage / profiling
*.profraw
/coverage
